# Smart Agriculture App - Detailed System Design

## 1. Database Schema Design (Entity Relationship)

Below is a normalized structure for a relational database (e.g., PostgreSQL) with specialized document storage (e.g., MongoDB) for media/content.

### Core Tables

#### `users` (Relational)
| Column Name | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `id` | UUID | Primary Key |
| `phone_number` | VARCHAR | Unique ID for Login |
| `username` | VARCHAR | Farmer's Name |
| `location_lat` | FLOAT | Latitude for regional data |
| `location_long` | FLOAT | Longitude for regional data |
| `preferred_lang`| VARCHAR | Regional language setting |
| `land_details` | JSONB | Size, soil type, history |

#### `crops` (Relational/Lookup)
| Column Name | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `id` | SERIAL | Primary Key |
| `name` | VARCHAR | Name (Paddy, Wheat, etc.) |
| `category` | VARCHAR | Grain, Fruit, Vegetable |
| `guide_data` | JSONB | Varieties, Duration, soil reqs |

#### `shops` (Relational)
| Column Name | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `id` | UUID | Primary Key |
| `name` | VARCHAR | Shop Name |
| `location` | POINT | Geo-spatial coordinates |
| `rating` | FLOAT | Avg User Rating |
| `is_organic` | BOOLEAN | Focus on organic/natural |

#### `inventory` (Relational)
| Column Name | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `shop_id` | UUID | FK to Shops |
| `product_name` | VARCHAR | Product Name |
| `stock_level` | INT | Current Availability |
| `price` | FLOAT | Unit Price |
| `discount` | INT | % Discount |

### AI & Media Modules (Document Store - MongoDB)

#### `media_collection`
- `media_id`: UUID
- `title`: String
- `video_url`: String (S3 Link)
- `tags`: Array
- `likes_count`: Int

#### `ai_disease_logs`
- `user_id`: UUID
- `image_url`: String
- `detected_disease`: String
- `confidence`: Float
- `suggested_treatment`: String
- `timestamp`: DateTime

---

## 2. UI Module Suggestions

### Home Dashboard (The "Command Center")
- **Layout**: Simple 3x3 Grid or Large Vertical Cards.
- **Top Section**: "Agri-Weather" (Current Temp, Humidity, Rain Probability).
- **Center Section**: "Smart Reminders" (e.g., "Water your Paddy in 2 hours").
- **Bottom Section**: "Market Trends" (Price ticker for top crops).

### AI Assistant & Camera
- **Interaction**: One-tap "Camera" icon from any screen.
- **Assistant**: Voice-to-text enabled chat interface for farmers who prefer speaking over typing.
- **Real-time overlays**: Highlight diseased areas on the camera screen using AR frames.

### Market & Prediction Module
- **Visuals**: Clean, non-distracting Line Graphs showing 'Past 3 Months' vs 'Next 1 Month'.
- **Action**: "Best time to sell" indicator badge.

### Learning & Media
- **UI**: Vertical scrolling feed (similar to TikTok/Instagram Reels) but focused solely on agriculture tips.
- **Engagement**: Share buttons for WhatsApp (Crucial for regional farmer communities).

### Expert Consultation
- **Grid**: Profile cards of experts with "Available Now" green dot.
- **History**: Chat-like history of past consultations for reference.

---

## 3. Localization Strategy
- **Framework**: Use i18next for multi-language support.
- **Fallback**: Default to English but prompt for regional language on first boot.
- **Interface**: Minimize text reliance, use universally recognized agriculture icons (Plow, Water Drop, Sun, Shield for Disease).
